Interface IPlugIn<M extends IIndexManager,S>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface IPlugIn<M extends IIndexManager,S>
    Interface for a "plug in" that can be registered with a Journal. TODO Support at IIndexManager interface? E.g., for the federation as well as the journal.
